,"1276":"1276","Pembrokeshire, Wales":"Pembrokeshire, Galles","Llangwm, Pembrokeshire, Wales":"Llangwm, Pembrokeshire, Galles","Roche, Pembrokeshire, Wales":"Pembrokeshire, Galles","Roch, Pembrokeshire, Wales":"Roch, Pembrokeshire, Pays de Galles, Royaume-Uni","lifeSummary":"Joan De La Roche est née en 1279, à Llangwm, Pembrokeshire, Pays de Galles, Royaume-Uni, fille de Sir Thomas De La Roche, Baron Roche of Fermoy and Roch, Sheriff of Cork, MP. Elle a épousé Sir David de la Roche of Llangwm en 1315, à Pembrokeshire, Pays de Galles, Royaume-Uni. Ils ont eu au moins 1 fils. Elle est décédée en 1316, à Pembrokeshire, Galles, à l’âge de 37 ans."},"de":{"1279–1316":"1279–1316","1272–1360":"1272–1360","1276–1314":"1276–1314","1280–1314":"1280–1314","1281–1324":"1281–1324","1285–1360":"1285–1360","1287–Female":"1287–Verstorben","1290–1324":"1290–1324","1282–1316":"1282–1316","1316–1376":"1316–1376","1250–1314":"1250–1314","1285":"1285","1250":"1250","1360":"1360","1272":"1272","1282":"1282","1281":"1281","1280":"1280","1290":"1290","1316":"1316","1315":"1315","1314":"1314","1324":"1324","1279":"1279","about 1316":"um 1316","1376":"1376","1287":"1287","1276":"1276","Pembrokeshire, Wales":"Pembrokeshire, Wales","Llangwm, Pembrokeshire, Wales":"Llangwm, Pembrokeshire, Wales","Roche, Pembrokeshire, Wales":"Pembrokeshire, Wales","Roch, Pembrokeshire, Wales":"Roch, Pembrokeshire, Wales, United Kingdom","lifeSummary":"Joan De La Roche wurde 1279 in Llangwm, Pembrokeshire, Wales, United Kingdom, als Tochter von Sir Thomas De La Roche, Baron Roche of Fermoy and Roch, Sheriff of Cork, MP geboren. Sie hat 1315 in Pembrokeshire, Wales, United Kingdom Sir David de la Roche of Llangwm geheiratet. Sie hatten mindestens 1 Sohn. Sie starb 1316 im Alter von 37 Jahren in Pembrokeshire, Wales."},"ht":{"1279–1316":"1279–1316","1272–1360":"1272–1360","1276–1314":"1276–1314","1280–1314":"1280–1314","1281–1324":"1281–1324","1285–1360":"1285–1360","1287–Female":"1287–Desede","1290–1324":"1290–13